nrLLe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=d1dd221a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AWVisa/posts/387724169288602</a><br />\n醫學影像學 Medical Imaging:-<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AWVisa/posts/522400089154342\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAWVisa%2Fposts%2F522400089154342&d=oSiF6q%2BHtSOEBVfNLUnrLLe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=11793477\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AWVisa/posts/522400089154342</a><br />\n驗光 Optometry:-<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AWVisa/posts/524973802230304\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAWVisa%2Fposts%2F524973802230304&d=oSiF6q%2BHtSOEBVfNLUnrLLe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=a4d02e75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AWVisa/posts/524973802230304</a>"},{"pid":"6b409c1b29ab015f1daf6a332a9a39616fa844b9","tid":2529962,"uid":30199,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T05:56:09.000Z","msg":"雖然小弟係做澳洲移民，但係憑良心講，依家既澳洲移民政策的確比起其他移民熱門國家都要黎得uncompetitive，唔單只HK 5年簽證之後既安排，其實全球性既技術或投資移民政策都係一樣咁唔清唔楚同慢人一拍。<br />\n<br />\n所以真係除非對澳洲有愛，有感情，有親戚，如果唔係真係可以考慮UK/Canada。好多人問完我覺得移民澳洲難都會老實同我講決定去UK/Canada，講真唔會有hard-feeling。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n姑勿論係由於政治，外交，定本土情況所限，我覺得ScoMo政府單單係移民政策呢一項已經曝露出短視無遠見既弊病。疫情總會有完結既一日 (應該係)，之後好有可能會係經濟反彈期，到時先係最需要人/移民/專才/外來投資，但係澳洲係呢個時候已經起步比其他大國要慢的話真係擔心未來會係咩情況。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d49a752a87d3ce5d46784eb179ff4d88ac1ea8f","tid":2529962,"uid":30199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T05:58:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n等上訴結果，如果唔係要take the case further。具體要點做我都要研究下。"},{"pid":"fa93c9d32c84d496076d1ce6a912e2a48ec7494d","tid":2529962,"uid":30199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T05:58:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你好，由我巴<br />\n想請問ACS Skill Assessment個邊，對於文件file size同dpi嘅要求有幾嚴格？按照guideline，要求文件要超過300dpi，又只可以1份pdf。<br />\n但online submit嘅時候，又可以upload唔超過5MB嘅文件，其實係唔係比架？<br />\n<br />\n我有幾份文件大概都係3.x MB到 4.x MB之間，唔知點樣可以唔降低dpi而又減到size🙈🙈</blockquote>無記錯係upload唔到太大既file。3-4mb唔係5mb以下？</blockquote>但佢要求係3MB，所以想知其實係唔係一定要跟，還是upload到就得</blockquote><br />\nUpload到就得。"},{"pid":"45245993e7d63d412ed48cadf93ccfacebbcfc50","tid":2529962,"uid":30199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T05:59:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>唉同埋好似會斷埋485 <br />\n呢個所謂香港人優待嘅plan....因為476就唔可以再apply 485 不過依家情況好似都唔明朗</blockquote><em>因為476就唔可以再apply 485</em><br />\n<br />\nSource?</blockquote>唔好意思 想請教埋 如果係485 holder 嘅subsequent entry (?) 即係485 holder 嘅屋企人可唔可以係澳洲返full time ?</blockquote><br />\n可以。"},{"pid":"b114e0dfd02a98e8b65c803ed55e67fa1ac01595","tid":2529962,"uid":30199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T06:00:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唉同埋好似會斷埋485 <br />\n呢個所謂香港人優待嘅plan....因為476就唔可以再apply 485 不過依家情況好似都唔明朗</blockquote><em>因為476就唔可以再apply 485</em><br />\n<br />\nSource?</blockquote><a href=\"https://immi.homeaffairs.gov.au/visas/getting-a-visa/visa-listing/temporary-graduate-485/graduate-work#Eligibility\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimmi.homeaffairs.gov.au%2Fvisas%2Fgetting-a-visa%2Fvisa-listing%2Ftemporary-graduate-485%2Fgraduate-work%23Eligibility&d=oSiF6q%2BHtSOEBVfNLUnrLLe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=ad1fe581\" target=\"_blank\">https://immi.homeaffairs.gov.au/visas/getting-a-visa/visa-listing/temporary-graduate-485/graduate-work#Eligibility</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://